<h1>About KhumaloCraft</h1>
<p>KhumaloCraft Emporium was founded by James Khumalo, a visionary entrepreneur with a passion for connecting global artisans with customers who appreciate handcrafted products. Our mission is to provide a platform where artisans from around the world can showcase their work and sustain their craft.</p>

